1
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:06,359
Hun Mie Sheng unleashes his hidden
five-star Dou Saint power.

2
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:09,599
He’s determined to seize the
Demonic Flame’s origin from Xiao Yan.

3
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:12,079
Luckily, Xiao Chen intervenes in time.

4
00:00:12,080 --> 00:00:13,279
And defeats him.

5
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:17,959
Refusing to accept defeat, Hun Mie Sheng
summons the five-star Dou Saint, Soul Demon Elder.

6
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:22,279
At the same time, the six-star Dou Saint
and Pill Tower Ancestor also appears.

7
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:26,799
The Pill Tower Ancestor reveals the truth—
the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame was sealed on purpose.

8
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,159
Forcing the flame to reveal itself.

9
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:32,839
Enraged, the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame
summons the Ancient Refining Heaven Array.

10
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:34,799
Intending to refine everyone present.

11
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,719
At the critical moment...

12
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:39,039
The Pure Lotus Demon Saint
possesses Xiao Yan’s body.

13
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:40,879
And saves everyone.

14
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,879
Pure Lotus Demon Saint...

15
00:00:56,560 --> 00:01:00,079
The legendary peak expert from back then,
said to be closest to becoming a Dou Di.

16
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,200
How did Xiao Yan...

17
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,719
manage to summon the Pure Lotus Demon Saint?

18
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,399
This Demon Saint isn’t in soul form.

19
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,559
It looks more like a residual image.

20
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:10,919
What’s going on?

21
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:12,919
Could it be because of that remnant map?

22
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:16,239
When Xiao Yan collected all the
remnant map pieces...

23
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,039
A ray of light shot into his body.

24
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,639
What do we do now?

25
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:23,239
The Pure Lotus Demon Saint has taken over
Brother Xiao Yan’s body.

26
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,479
If anything goes wrong...

27
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,919
Brother Xiao Yan will be the one
who suffers the most.

28
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,239
Don’t panic.

29
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,239
He will save us.

30
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,679
I don’t think he means any harm.

31
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,919
His target...

32
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,839
should be the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame.

33
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,360
You old bastard...

34
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,560
How is this possible?

35
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,239
How can you still be alive?

36
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,319
After thousands of years of sealing...

37
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:53,439
It seems it still couldn’t erase
the madness in your heart.

38
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,640
Damn you!

39
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,799
Pure Lotus Demon Saint...

40
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,679
You ungrateful bastard!

41
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,159
I helped you so much...

42
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,359
Yet you repaid my kindness by sealing me away!

43
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,119
Serves you right to have been devoured
and killed in the end!

44
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,479
This grand array was created by you personally.

45
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,000
Today...

46
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:10,879
You shall taste its power as well!

47
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,959
You shall taste its power as well!

48
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,680
Die!

49
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
You old fool!

50
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,760
Refine!

51
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,680
Stabilize!

52
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,719
That you turned out so violent...

53
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,279
I bear some responsibility as well.

54
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,439
But if I had let you leave freely...

55
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,399
This world...

56
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,119
would have faced a great catastrophe.

57
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,319
I created the Ancient Refining Heaven Array.

58
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,039
When it comes to understanding it...

59
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,839
You are still far beneath me.

60
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,640
Old bastard!

61
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,839
I’ll fight you to the death!

62
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,399
Demonic Flame—World Annihilation!

63
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,679
Hurry and leave this place.

64
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,359
If the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame
fully erupts...

65
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,239
None of you will survive.

66
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,600
Go, quickly!

67
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,479
Miss...

68
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,559
We should leave at once too.

69
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,759
But Brother Xiao Yan’s mind
has been taken over by the Demon Saint.

70
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,119
If we just leave like this...

71
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,159
I won’t feel at ease.

72
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,079
Stop worrying about that!

73
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:18,799
Hurry and go!

74
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,719
Staying here won’t help anything.

75
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:23,439
Since the Demon Saint Senior has borrowed
Xiao Yan’s body...

76
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,559
He won’t harm him.

77
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:25,760
Let’s go too.

78
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:49,999
Miss...

79
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,919
You...

80
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,799
I’m going back to stay with Brother Xiao Yan.

81
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,479
Miss, please don’t be reckless!

82
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,599
Going back now is no different from suicide!

83
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,399
Besides, Miss should understand even better...

84
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,759
What you mean to the Ancient Clan.

85
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,120
Enough!

86
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,520
All these years...

87
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,319
I’ve always followed the clan’s arrangements.

88
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,599
Whenever Brother Xiao Yan needed help most...

89
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,759
I was never there.

90
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,759
Now that Brother Xiao Yan is right in front
of me facing mortal danger...

91
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,839
You still want me to follow the rules?

92
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,200
I refuse!

93
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,200
Miss...

94
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,799
When you return, please tell Father...

95
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,120
This time...

96
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,519
Allow Xun’er to be willful once.

97
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,399
When I first met you all those years ago...

98
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,519
You were as pure as an infant.

99
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:34,639
I granted you spiritual awareness
so you could possess human thoughts.

100
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,799
But the path you chose to walk
is completely different from what I envisioned.

101
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,159
Diametrically opposed.

102
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,239
How I grow...

103
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,639
is my own affair.

104
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,000
Old thing!

105
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,719
You interfere too much.

106
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:49,039
I simply do not wish for you
to sink into self-destruction.

107
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,839
I was the one who made you this way.

108
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,919
So let me be the one to end this.

109
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,239
Pure Lotus Demon Saint!

110
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:08,359
You heartless bastard!

111
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,439
I will never let you have your way.

112
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,079
When my end was near,

113
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,199
I did consider erasing your memories.

114
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,359
But I could not bring myself to do it.

115
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,319
Hence, I sealed you,

116
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:29,439
hoping to dissolve the tyranny
and killing intent in your heart.

117
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,759
But now it seems,

118
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:36,279
that thousands of years of sealing
have only intensified your hatred.

119
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,159
Since that is the case,

120
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,399
Ancient Refining Heaven Formation—

121
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,440
Strip!

122
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,600
Stop!

123
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,199
You old bastard!

124
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,599
Stop right now!

125
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,639
Without memories,

126
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,919
without spiritual intellect,

127
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,039
what difference is there from killing me?

128
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,440
Hypocrite!

129
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,479
Your temperament

130
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,919
is utterly brutal.

131
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,319
Now, having received my inheritance,

132
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,919
if I let you break the seal,

133
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,039
it will surely spell disaster.

134
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,639
The calamity was drawn by me,

135
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:30,319
so naturally, it must end with me.

136
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,719
No...

137
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,720
Return my true body!

138
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,760
Give me back my body!

139
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,120
Master...

140
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,159
Master...

141
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,519
Little Demon, I know I was wrong.

142
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,839
Spare me this once.

143
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,239
I will definitely change!

144
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,160
Master...

145
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,959
For the sake of our many years together,

146
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,319
please let me go.

147
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,039
Xun'er...

148
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,399
Why are you still here?

149
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,760
Brother Xiao Yan.

150
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,320
This time,

151
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,919
I must stay with you.

152
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,440
You...

153
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,880
Stand behind me.

154
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:33,519
I have lived my life without disciples or sons,

155
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,919
alone in solitude.

156
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,719
From beginning to end,

157
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,679
you have been the one closest to me.

158
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:41,159
Even if you eventually backslash me,

159
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:42,919
I do not hate you.

160
00:08:42,920 --> 00:08:44,879
But I hate you!

161
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,839
Die!

162
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,079
Old thing!

163
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:53,959
You've been fooled again!

164
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,599
You've been tricked once more!

165
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,559
This appearance...

166
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,959
is just like that day.

167
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,480
Little Demon,

168
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,479
follow me.

169
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,600
Together,

170
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,279
we will dissipate forever
between heaven and earth.

171
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,039
No!

172
00:09:18,063 --> 00:09:55,463
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

173
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:56,959
Demon Saint Senior...

174
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,880
Go well.

175
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,359
Brother Xiao Yan,

176
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,360
look.

177
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,680
This is...

178
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,839
The source of the Demon Flame.

179
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,679
This Pure Lotus Demon Fire...

180
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,279
seems different from before.

181
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:28,479
The Demon Saint Senior erased its memories

182
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,480
and even its spiritual intellect.

183
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,399
The Demon Flame now

184
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,439
is as pure as a newborn.

185
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,959
What now?

186
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,079
Now that the space channel has dispersed,

187
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,039
with our current abilities,

188
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,439
we likely cannot tear apart
this space.

189
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,120
Since we can't get out,

190
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,799
then I shall refine the Demon Flame
right here.

191
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,399
Does Brother Xiao Yan have confidence?

192
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,600
Less than fifty percent.

193
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,679
It can't be helped.

194
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,439
If we took the source of the Demon Flame out,

195
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,559
it would surely invite the covetousness
of countless people.

196
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,639
Even if we fled to the Gu Clan for refuge,

197
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,999
it would bring great trouble.

198
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:08,079
And this space was hand-crafted
by the Demon Saint himself;

199
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,639
almost no one can break in.

200
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,999
It is the perfect location
to refine the Demon Flame.

201
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,759
Besides, we can't leave for a long while.

202
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,639
Perhaps some will assume we met with misfortune.

203
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,119
That would save us quite a bit of trouble.

204
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,039
Miss...

205
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,639
We're finished.

206
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,559
We actually left the Miss behind.

207
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,159
If we return to the Gu Clan like this,

208
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,279
I dread to think what kind of scolding we'll face.

209
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,039
Elder,

210
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,359
do not blame yourself.

211
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,399
Xun'er insisted on staying with Xiao Yan.

212
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,759
Even if we reacted in time, it would have been useless.

213
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:47,319
The Gu Clan has suffered a great loss this time.

214
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,119
Just two youngsters...

215
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,799
Is it worth such a fuss?

216
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:56,039
Having missed the Pure Lotus Demon Flame this time,

217
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,399
I hope the Palace Master will carefully consider

218
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,519
how to report back to the Clan Leader.

219
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,039
In the meantime,

220
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,239
don't let the Tianfu Alliance live too comfortably.

221
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,079
Well?

222
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,080
Any news?

223
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:20,679
Negative.

224
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,879
That place has the seals of the Pure Lotus Demon Saint.

225
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,199
I cannot sense their location.

226
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:25,479
However,

227
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,919
Elder Gu need not worry.

228
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,519
With Sister Xun'er and Xiao Yan together,

229
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,199
nothing untoward will happen.

230
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,359
Otherwise,

231
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,759
Xiao Yan would go utterly mad.

232
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,079
The Dragon Seal

233
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,399
would not remain so calm either.

234
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:40,519
Then I must trouble Lady Ziyan to keep watching for us.

235
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,239
Now that this has happened,

236
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:44,079
I must return to the Gu Clan immediately

237
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,199
to report this matter.

238
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,279
Rest assured.

239
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,879
I have people monitoring this area.

240
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,199
At the first sign of trouble,

241
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,639
we will notify the Gu Clan.

242
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,880
Many thanks.

243
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,399
Brother Xiao Yan,

244
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,519
are you ready?

245
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,799
This formation is the Blazing Cold Grand Array.

246
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,839
It can suppress the Demon Flame to some extent.

247
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,759
Xun'er,

248
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,319
I am about to begin refining the Demon Flame.

249
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,400
It's working.

250
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:37,920
Brother Xiao Yan...

251
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:42,639
For this day,

252
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:44,999
I have strived for so many years.

253
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,240
This little pain

254
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,799
cannot stop me.

255
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:53,280
Burn!

256
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,520
Refine for me!

257
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:28,400
If this continues,

258
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,359
Brother Xiao Yan is certain to die.

259
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,359
Xun'er...

260
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,360
You...

261
00:15:58,640 --> 00:15:59,640
Brother Xiao Yan,

262
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:01,040
this time,

263
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,479
Xun'er will help you.

264
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:04,799
Together, we will refine it.

265
00:16:04,823 --> 00:16:48,223
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

